{
  "stem": "214.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know if she was older then I am now, but, you know, of course, she was a very old woman.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and my father has one sister, [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Edka, ?] and she lived-- they all lived in Skierniewice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One of her daughters survived, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Merta ?], who lives now in Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as I say, it was a very-- I suppose, a Hasidic, for me, a very average home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not rich, and we were not starving.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I suppose [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know when you grow up, you really don't pay so much attention.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, we were considered-- we were going to private schools, because my parents didn't want my brothers to be going to-- there was this cheder, which was also secular in Lodz, called the [?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Lisatz. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all the-- again, called, quote, unquote, 'aristocratic Hasidic kids.' The boys were-- were going there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then there was my oldest sister, who went to a regular gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it also was owned, I think, by [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Gashiniska ?] was the name, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Gashiniska ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nicwanoa. ?] When I started kindergarten, I think maybe for two years kindergarten in the first class with all German, Polish, I started with the [?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Gashiniska ?] but then Bais Yaakov, the regular Bais Yaakov school was open, and we all were transferred there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- and life was neither exciting, neither not exciting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We-- you know, the Jewish holidays, and we were supposedly-- you know, we were not allowed to go down and play in the yard.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know if you know those Polish yards now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was just-- just like one big garbage pail, but it was kept.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We-- we did not have a house.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
